# License & Attribution

Sermon transcripts, titles, scripture references, and metadata in this repository are derived from the published works of Tim Keller, available at [gospelinlife.com](https://gospelinlife.com), the official sermon archive of his ministry.

## Fair use

Most quotes and references to Gospel in Life content are permitted under the [fair use doctrine](https://www.copyright.gov/fair-use/index.html) of U.S. copyright law, provided they are cited properly. This repository was built for non-commercial study and to enable LLM-grounded responses that explicitly attribute their sources back to the original sermons.

If you use the wiki or raw transcripts in this repo:

- Cite the sermon by title, date, and scripture reference.
- Do not redistribute the underlying audio recordings.
- Direct people to [gospelinlife.com](https://gospelinlife.com) as the canonical source.

## Permissions questions

For questions about what is covered under Gospel in Life's content policy, contact: **support@gospelinlife.com**.

